# Code Owners for automation-exercise repository
#
# This file defines who is responsible for code in this repository.
# When a pull request is opened, GitHub will automatically request reviews
# from the designated code owners.
#
# Syntax: <file-pattern> @username @org/team-name
#
# For more information, see:
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

